snippet.textDisplay: Imagine what it would be if the Queen Of Melody Madam Noor Jahan is performing live in the coke studio. Cant get a better view. We miss her. She was the best. Sir Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan and Madam Noor Jahan was the pride of Pakistan. Rahat Fateh Ali Khan is continuing the legacy of Nusrat in a small way but I wish that there should have been someone to continue the legacy of Madam Noor Jahan. This song is emotional and touchy. Thanks Coke studio. Cant get a better tribute to legend.
